{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So finally, I don't know how many hours it took or maybe took a day or whatever, we arrived to that new apartment where-- where we-- that was our new home now for hiding out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow the word goes very fast, you know, people telling stuff when you don't have newspaper or radio or somehow one person talks to another, and the news goes very fast.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we learned that after we left this building where we were on the fourth floor and-- and all the streetcars were full with ammunition, a bomb did hit the streetcar, and the whole neighborhood disappeared.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was leveled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So here's another interesting thing in my life story, so to speak, that when you wonder as why things happening sometimes to you in life, immediately you have no explanation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just like when I had this urge to go to the movies, which finally saved my-- my mother and sister's life, here again, this lady broke down and that saved our lives, because on the fourth floor, we would have been buried with five trillion tons of, you know, bricks and the whole building.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We would have been still under there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- so-- but we survived that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So from the bakery, you went to this place, and then from this place you moved to the-- across the river.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But tell me, I want to go back to the bakery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why did you say that if you were doing a play, you would be-- it would be a happy ending to have everybody dying.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't understand that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said it would not be a happy ending.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whose name was Jan Kadar, and I met him in 1940s.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
